OL,6,CG1983FBecause of industrial action,
OL,7,FBBC One was unable to broadcast World
OL,8,FCup Cricket. An on-screen apology
OL,9,Fcaption pointed viewers to live
OL,10,Fcommentary of the match - between
OL,11,FEngland and Sri Lanka - on BBC Radio 3
OL,12,FMedium Wave.
