OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2017FThe BBC News at Ten is struck
OL,7,Fdown by technical problems, when the
OL,8,Fprogramme's playout and graphics
OL,9,Fsystems crash moments before going on
OL,10,Fair. The programme was still put to air
OL,11,Fon the BBC News channel and BBC One,
OL,12,Fwith presenter Huw Edwards left sitting
OL,13,Fat the main presenting desk, in
OL,14,Fsilence.
OL,15,
OL,16,FBBC One quickly switched to a programme
OL,17,Fmenu and then apology caption. Huw was
OL,18,Fleft on air on the BBC News channel for
OL,19,Fthe duration of the fault. The
OL,20,Fprogramme got under way after 4
OL,21,Fminutes. Huw apologised for the
OL,22,Ftechnical problems just before he
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
